episodes.title: Laurel County schools cancel picture day amid concerns over vendor’s alleged Epstein ties
episodes.description:
Picture day is canceled for Laurel County Public Schools students as parents across the nation are concerned about a former CEO who invested in Lifetouch’s parent company and his alleged ties to Jeffrey Epstein.
